data.description: Come tour this beautiful 3 bed, 2.5 bath corner lot single family home! As you enter the home, there’s an open foyer which houses the downstairs half bath as well as the coat closet! The open floorplan that greets you through the foyer is all you could ask for! From the living room to the dining area to the kitchen, there are no impeding walls and the open space allows for an easy flow!  As you go up the stairs, the loft sits open and outside of the 3 bedrooms as well as the upstairs laundry room! This home has it all! If you’re looking for a starter home, this could be the one! If you’re looking for a good investment property, this too could be the one! Add this one to your list and check it out!
